gle: GLE - Graphics Layout Engine
gle:
gle: GLE is a graphics language that produces PostScript, EPS, PDF, PNG,
gle: or JPG ouput from a simple script file. The GLE scripting language
gle: is full featured with variables, subroutines, logic control, looping,
gle: and graphing tools. It is great for plotting and charting data.
gle: 
gle: GLE can create very complex output with text and graphics (including
gle: graphs and charts) from a simple plain text file.
gle:
